>著，<span class="_ _6"></span>但所有这些都对众生有利。<span class="_ _8"></span>我常将佛</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y24b ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">法比喻成药，<span class="_ _6"></span>西方的药、<span class="_ _8"></span>东方的药、<span class="_ _6"></span>藏地的药、<span class="_ _8"></span>印度的药等</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y24c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">等，<span class="_ _6"></span>药虽不同，<span class="_ _8"></span>但对身体都有治疗作用，<span class="_ _6"></span>同样，<span class="_ _8"></span>不同传承的</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y24d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">佛法，也可以治疗不同众生内心的疾病。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c h4 y24e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">所以，<span class="_ _10"></span>佛教的利美思想，<span class="_ _10"></span>非常合理，<span class="_ _10"></span>值得大家认真思考。<span class="_ _c"></span> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
